<!-- ----ViewStromzaehler.vue----------------khartinger----- -->
<!-- 2023-01-02: new                                         -->

<template>
  <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 -30 400 500">
    <rect class="w2Background" x="0" y="-30" width="400" height="530" />
    <text class="ciFontRoom" :x="1.8*dx" :y="0.0*dy">Stromzähler</text>
    <!--
    <CiTextarea :x="0.5*dx" :y="0.17*dy" sid="imgstrom" :border="2" :fx="1.5" :fy="0.5"></CiTextarea>
    <CiTimeDate :x="1*dx" :y="0*dy" sid="timeDate_1" :border="0"></CiTimeDate>
    <CiTextarea :x="0*dx" :y="0*dy" sid="watt" :border="3" :fx="1.0" :fy="1.0"></CiTextarea>
    -->
    <CiButton :x="0.5*dx" :y="0.17*dy" sid="imgstrom" :border="2" lines="1" :fx="1.8" :fy="0.5"></CiButton>

    <image :x="0*dx" :y="0*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img0.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`" />
    <image :x="1*dx" :y="0*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img1.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="2*dx" :y="0*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img2.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="3*dx" :y="0*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img3.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="0*dx" :y="1*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img4.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="1*dx" :y="1*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img5.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="2*dx" :y="1*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img6.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="3*dx" :y="1*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img7.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="0*dx" :y="2*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img8.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <image :x="1*dx" :y="2*dy" :height="1*dx" :width="1*dy" :href="`/haus_img/img9.jpg?cacheBust=${cacheBust}`"  />
    <CiTextarea :x="3.5*dx" :y="2.5*dy" sid="watt" :border="3" :fx="1.0" :fy="1.0"></CiTextarea>
  </svg>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { Geo } from '../classes/Geo'
import CiButton from '@/components/CiButton.vue'
import CiTextarea from '@/components/CiTextarea.vue'
// import CiTimeDate from '@/components/CiTimeDate.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'ViewStromzaehler',
  data: () => ({
    cacheBust: 0,
    intervalId: 0
  }),
  components: {
    // CiTimeDate,
    CiTextarea,
    CiButton
  },
  mounted: function () {
    this.intervalId = (setInterval(() => {
      this.cacheBust = Date.now()
    }, 2500)) as any
  },
  unmounted: function () {
    clearInterval(this.intervalId)
  },
  computed: {
    geo: function (): Geo {
      const geo1 = new Geo(0, 0)
      return geo1
    },
    dx: function (): number { return (this.geo.dxo) },
    dy: function (): number { return (this.geo.dyo) }
  },
  methods: {
    showErdgeschoss: function () {
      console.log('CLICK - showErdgeschoss', '')
      this.$router.push({ name: 'Erdgeschoss' }).catch((e) => { console.error('ViewStromzaehler: ERROR:', e) })
    }
  }
})
</script>

<style scoped>
.w2Background {fill: blue; }
.w2Font1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; fill: yellow; color: lightgreen; font-family: "DejaVu Sans Mono","monospace"; white-space: pre; }

</style>
